sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant VAR as VA Reconciler
    participant SatEng as Saturation Engine<br/>30s polling
    participant Prom as Prometheus / Thanos<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant vLLM as vLLM Servers
    participant Cache as Decision Cache<br/>In-Memory
    participant Act as Actuator
    participant Metrics as /metrics Endpoint<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HPA as HPA / KEDA
    participant Deploy as Deployments / LWS

    Note over User,Deploy: Flow 1: Saturation-Based Autoscaling Loop

    User->>K8s: Create VariantAutoscaling CR
    K8s->>VAR: Watch event (VA created)
    VAR->>VAR: Register variant for optimization

    loop Every 30 seconds
        SatEng->>Prom: PromQL query (KV cache, queue depth, tokens)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA token)
        Prom->>vLLM: Scrape vllm:kv_cache_usage_perc,<br/>num_requests_waiting, cache_config_info
        vLLM-->>Prom: Metrics response
        Prom-->>SatEng: Query results (HTTPS response)
        SatEng->>SatEng: Analyze saturation (V1/V2/Queueing)
        SatEng->>SatEng: Run CostAware/GreedyByScore optimizer
        SatEng->>Cache: Write VariantDecision
        Cache->>VAR: Trigger via GenericEvent channel
        VAR->>K8s: Patch VA status (desired replicas)<br/>Auth: SA token
        VAR->>Act: Emit scaling metrics
        Act->>Metrics: Update wva_desired_replicas,<br/>wva_desired_ratio, wva_current_replicas
    end

    Prom->>Metrics: Scrape /metrics<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    HPA->>Prom: Read wva_desired_ratio<br/>Auth: SA token
    HPA->>K8s: Scale Deployment/LWS<br/>Auth: SA token
    K8s->>Deploy: Update replicas

    Note over User,Deploy: Flow 2: Scale-From-Zero Detection

    participant SFZ as Scale-From-Zero Engine<br/>100ms polling
    participant EPP as EPP Pods<br/>Endpoint Picker

    loop Every 100ms
        SFZ->>EPP: Scrape flow_control_queue_size<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (EPP metrics token)
        EPP-->>SFZ: Queue metrics response
        alt Pending requests for idle variant (replicas=0)
            SFZ->>K8s: Scale subresource 0→1<br/>Auth: SA token
            K8s->>Deploy: Set replicas=1
            SFZ->>Cache: Write decision + trigger channel
            Cache->>VAR: Trigger reconciliation
        end
    end
